{"type":"answer","id":339813,"parentType":"question","parentId":30955,"uid":26862,"contents":"中共国现在很流行歧义谬误。<br>\n你用某词语想表达 A 意思，他却理解为 B 意思。<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/AuZJo9x.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/AuZJo9x.png\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/AuZJo9x.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a><br>\n在政治、经济上造新的词义，甚至还能与国际上的意思相反。鲁迅与梁启超的棺材板压不住了。","date":"2020-09-14","agreeCount":3,"discussionCount":0}